column1: Daily Weather Observations for Adelaide Airport, South Australia for December 2019
Prepared at 13:02 UTC on Saturday 10 October 2020   IDCJDW5001.201912
Observations are made about 1 km east of the coast.
Some cloud observations are from automated equipment; these are somewhat different to those made by a human observer and may not appear every day.
Observations were drawn from Adelaide Airport {station 023034}
